TITLE: Accessing AI Model Inference Server with Java and Quarkus
DESCRIPTION: Java code snippet using Quarkus framework to interact with the AI model inference server. This example shows how to send a request and handle the response in a Java application.
SOURCE: https://github.com/podman-desktop/podman-desktop/blob/main/website/docs/ai-lab/start-inference-server.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
@Path("/chat")
public class ChatResource {

    @Inject
    ChatService chatService;

    @POST
    @Consumes(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)
    @Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)
    public Response chat(ChatRequest request) {
        String response = chatService.chat(request);
        return Response.ok(response).build();
    }
}
```

