TITLE: JSON Schema for Warning Component Items in Onboarding (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: Outlines the properties and requirements for a warning list item in onboarding content. Mandatory fields are 'state', 'description', and (for 'command') both 'id' and 'title'. The 'docLinks' array supports documentation references grouped by category. The object is used by UI components rendering warnings or status messages. Must conform to this schema when populating context values for warnings.
