TITLE: Starting Podman Machine with Shell Commands - shell-session
DESCRIPTION: Starts the Podman machine after configuration, enabling it to run in rootful mode as set previously. Assumes Podman is installed and the machine was previously configured in rootful mode. Outputs startup progress and confirmation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/podman-desktop/podman-desktop/blob/main/website/docs/minikube/configuring-podman-for-minikube-on-windows.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: shell-session
CODE:
```
$ podman machine start
```

