TITLE: Connecting to Podman Machine Shell - Shell Script
DESCRIPTION: This shell command opens an interactive shell session inside the specified Podman machine. It assumes you have Podman installed and a valid machine name. The command enables users to perform administrative operations inside the dedicated Podman VM. No arguments other than the machine name are required; output is a shell prompt within the VM.
SOURCE: https://github.com/podman-desktop/podman-desktop/blob/main/website/docs/podman/adding-certificates-to-a-podman-machine.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
```sh\n$ podman machine ssh <machine_name>\n```
```

